                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>...Well, I think you get the idea—and why I didn't, you know, run with this. But hopefully at one point, you flashed a bit of a smile or even let out a tiny laugh. If not, sorry. I'll try harder next week.</p>
